{"tid":1442681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭又講大話，佢根本想國企主面攻入香港","createTime":"2019-08-11T04:32:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T08:33:38.000Z","uid":120377,"like":150,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"394b97216d8abb6713046f1c754a6c3cf2e86ba2","tid":1442681,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:32:59.000Z","msg":"你老味！<br />\n林鄭上午打香港經濟牌！<br />\n果頭就要阿爺出手搞香港企業！<br />\n國泰係香港係大公司！<br />\n佢居然連一句了解，協調對無！<br />\n仲話香港經濟，國際形象好重要！<br />\n香港經濟咪就係俾佢一手整死！<br />\n代表香港？佢應該多謝香港人！俾機會佢做傀儡特首！<br />\n如果唔係我地，佢只不過係一個普通公務員咋！<br />\n<br />\n國泰係香港品牌，代表香港係自由社會，我地全是香港人，真係好心痛同難過！<br />\n<br />\n國泰，今次真係四面受敵！孤軍作戰！真係唔可以有出錯！國泰衰咗香港企業就無自由！大古放棄國泰，國航就收購國泰！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n國泰頂撚住呀！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我愛國泰<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d1f597bd233463dc6a349c56fc4d6259f4cbcf8","tid":1442681,"uid":270912,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:33:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"18257ded73e1e4406fb9eac6a713f4dff90d682e","tid":1442681,"uid":120377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:33:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"713bab580d12216c64b3b06d5b014d92db35f2db","tid":1442681,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T04:36:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7XjQ517.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7XjQ517.jpg&h=8be1ffb4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【求置頂】我係811港島東集會搞手，請大家冇野做就黎維園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1441981/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n811。約定你 「深水埗」「港島東」遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1441682/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\